  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600236239853-AQOR0ULETZM86JSFTO7K/1a-2psnewyears730x350-600x287.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>It's a pretty exciting new year already for all of us at <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/whats-hot/%3Fpp%3D300\">Two Peas in a Bucket</a>, as we are joined by some new talented ladies.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600236266707-GQ6QYPX6W9O1Y090QBU7/1b-2psGGteam2013-600x302.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>So glad I had the <a href=\"https://amy-tan-z6av.squarespace.com/amy-tangerine/2012/08/a-day-at-the-two-peas-office.html\">unique opportunity last year to visit the Two Peas head office and warehouse</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600236297160-1I455M1ERLYYU1BF3M57/1c-gettingcraftygg-559x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.twopeasinabucket.com/gallery/member/305620-amytangerine/1880955-getting-crafty-at-2-peas/\">Getting Crafty</a> || copyright Two Peas In a Bucket Really excited about the announcement that there will be videos everyday (Monday-Saturday) featuring various topics. No doubt there will be plenty of inspiration to help you document your awesome life. I will continue to do <a href=\"http://static.squarespace.com/static/54763a73e4b0d25603e00ba7/54a756aae4b0f2d6f3befd4e/54a773e6e4b0f2d6f3c1d714/1420260326362/my365?format=original\">my 365 photo-a-day project</a> as I found it to be rewarding, fun and pretty easy most days. Even though I didn't finish putting together my monthly collages (and I may not actually ever finish), the groupings of photos were neat to see together.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600236329258-TXQE7HHDEDXXLRS0JMP5/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.twopeasinabucket.com/gallery/member/305620-amytangerine/1876499-this-is-my-wonderful-life-365everyday/\">This Is My Wonderful Life</a> || Copyright Two Peas In a Bucket Looking forward to being a part of the Garden Girls again this year!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
